4955 static int
4956 get_cursor_pos (T_REQ_HANDLE * req_handle, int offset, char origin)
4957 {
4958  if (origin == CCI_CURSOR_FIRST)
4959  {
4960  return offset;
4961  }
4962  else if (origin == CCI_CURSOR_LAST)
4963  {
4964  return (req_handle->num_tuple - offset + 1);
4965  }
4966  return (req_handle->cursor_pos + offset);
4967 }

4969 static int
4970 fetch_info_decode (char *buf, int size, int num_cols, T_TUPLE_VALUE ** tuple_value, T_FETCH_TYPE fetch_type,
4971  T_REQ_HANDLE * req_handle, T_CON_HANDLE * con_handle)
4972 {
4973  int remain_size = size;
4974  char *cur_p = buf;
4975  int err_code = 0;
4976  int num_tuple, i, j;
4977  T_TUPLE_VALUE *tmp_tuple_value = NULL;
4978 #if defined (WINDOWS)
4979  char *charset = con_handle->charset;
4980 #endif
4981 
4982  if (fetch_type == FETCH_FETCH || fetch_type == FETCH_COL_GET)
4983  {
4984  if (remain_size < 4)
4985  {
4986  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
4987  }
4988 
4989  NET_STR_TO_INT (num_tuple, cur_p);
4990  remain_size -= 4;
4991  cur_p += 4;
4992  }
4993  else
4994  {
4995  num_tuple = 1;
4996  }
4997 
4998  if (num_tuple < 0)
4999  {
5000  return 0;
5001  }
5002  else if (num_tuple == 0)
5003  {
5004  if (fetch_type == FETCH_FETCH && hm_get_broker_version (con_handle) >= CAS_PROTO_MAKE_VER (PROTOCOL_V5))
5005  {
5006  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_BYTE)
5007  {
5008  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5009  }
5010 
5011  NET_STR_TO_BYTE (req_handle->is_fetch_completed, cur_p);
5012  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5013  cur_p += NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5014  }
5015 
5016  return 0;
5017  }
5018 
5019  tmp_tuple_value = (T_TUPLE_VALUE *) MALLOC (sizeof (T_TUPLE_VALUE) * num_tuple);
5020  if (tmp_tuple_value == NULL)
5021  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
5022  memset ((char *) tmp_tuple_value, 0, sizeof (T_TUPLE_VALUE) * num_tuple);
5023 
5024  for (i = 0; i < num_tuple; i++)
5025  {
5026  if (fetch_type == FETCH_FETCH)
5027  {
5028  if (remain_size < 4)
5029  {
5030  err_code = CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5031  goto fetch_info_decode_error;
5032  }
5033  NET_STR_TO_INT (tmp_tuple_value[i].tuple_index, cur_p);
5034  cur_p += 4;
5035  remain_size -= 4;
5036 
5037  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_OBJECT)
5038  {
5039  err_code = CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5040  goto fetch_info_decode_error;
5041  }
5042  stream_to_obj (cur_p, &(tmp_tuple_value[i].tuple_oid));
5043  cur_p += NET_SIZE_OBJECT;
5044  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_OBJECT;
5045  }
5046 
5047  tmp_tuple_value[i].column_ptr = (char **) MALLOC (sizeof (char *) * num_cols);
5048  if (tmp_tuple_value[i].column_ptr == NULL)
5049  {
5050  err_code = CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
5051  goto fetch_info_decode_error;
5052  }
5053  memset (tmp_tuple_value[i].column_ptr, '\0', sizeof (char *) * num_cols);
5054 
5055 #if defined(WINDOWS)
5056  tmp_tuple_value[i].decoded_ptr = (char **) MALLOC (sizeof (char *) * num_cols);
5057  if (tmp_tuple_value[i].decoded_ptr == NULL)
5058  {
5059  err_code = CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
5060  goto fetch_info_decode_error;
5061  }
5062  memset (tmp_tuple_value[i].decoded_ptr, '\0', sizeof (char *) * num_cols);
5063 #endif
5064 
5065  for (j = 0; j < num_cols; j++)
5066  {
5067  int data_size;
5068  char *col_p;
5069 #if defined (WINDOWS)
5070  T_CCI_U_TYPE u_type;
5071 #endif
5072 
5073  col_p = cur_p;
5074  if (remain_size < 4)
5075  {
5076  err_code = CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5077  goto fetch_info_decode_error;
5078  }
5079  NET_STR_TO_INT (data_size, cur_p);
5080  remain_size -= 4;
5081  cur_p += 4;
5082 
5083  if (remain_size < data_size)
5084  {
5085  err_code = CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5086  goto fetch_info_decode_error;
5087  }
5088 
5089 #if defined (WINDOWS)
5090  if (charset != NULL)
5091  {
5092  u_type = get_basic_utype (req_handle->col_info[j].ext_type);
5093  }
5094 
5095  if (charset != NULL
5096  && (u_type == CCI_U_TYPE_CHAR || u_type == CCI_U_TYPE_STRING || u_type == CCI_U_TYPE_NCHAR
5097  || u_type == CCI_U_TYPE_VARNCHAR || u_type == CCI_U_TYPE_ENUM))
5098  {
5099  err_code = decode_result_col (col_p, data_size, &(tmp_tuple_value[i].column_ptr[j]), charset);
5100 
5101  if (err_code < 0)
5102  {
5103  goto fetch_info_decode_error;
5104  }
5105  else if (err_code == 0)
5106  {
5107  /* invalid character set. do not convert string */
5108  tmp_tuple_value[i].column_ptr[j] = col_p;
5109  }
5110  else
5111  {
5112  tmp_tuple_value[i].decoded_ptr[j] = tmp_tuple_value[i].column_ptr[j];
5113  }
5114  }
5115  else
5116  {
5117  tmp_tuple_value[i].column_ptr[j] = col_p;
5118  }
5119 #else
5120  tmp_tuple_value[i].column_ptr[j] = col_p;
5121 #endif
5122 
5123  if (data_size > 0)
5124  {
5125  cur_p += data_size;
5126  remain_size -= data_size;
5127  }
5128  } /* end of for j */
5129  } /* end of for i */
5130 
5131  if (fetch_type == FETCH_FETCH && hm_get_broker_version (con_handle) >= CAS_PROTO_MAKE_VER (PROTOCOL_V5))
5132  {
5133  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_BYTE)
5134  {
5135  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5136  }
5137 
5138  NET_STR_TO_BYTE (req_handle->is_fetch_completed, cur_p);
5139  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5140  cur_p += NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5141  }
5142 
5143  *tuple_value = tmp_tuple_value;
5144 
5145  return num_tuple;
5146 
5147 fetch_info_decode_error:
5148  if (tmp_tuple_value)
5149  {
5150  for (i = 0; i < num_tuple; i++)
5151  {
5152 #if defined (WINDOWS)
5153  if (tmp_tuple_value[i].decoded_ptr)
5154  {
5155  for (j = 0; j < num_cols; j++)
5156  {
5157  FREE_MEM (tmp_tuple_value[i].decoded_ptr[j]);
5158  }
5159 
5160  FREE_MEM (tmp_tuple_value[i].decoded_ptr);
5161  }
5162 #endif
5163  FREE_MEM (tmp_tuple_value[i].column_ptr);
5164  }
5165  FREE_MEM (tmp_tuple_value);
5166  }
5167  return err_code;
5168 }

5170 static void
5171 stream_to_obj (char *buf, T_OBJECT * obj)
5172 {
5173  int pageid;
5174  short volid, slotid;
5175 
5176  NET_STR_TO_INT (pageid, buf);
5177  NET_STR_TO_SHORT (slotid, buf + 4);
5178  NET_STR_TO_SHORT (volid, buf + 6);
5179 
5180  obj->pageid = pageid;
5181  obj->slotid = slotid;
5182  obj->volid = volid;
5183 }

5185 static int
5186 get_data_set (T_CCI_U_EXT_TYPE u_ext_type, char *col_value_p, T_SET ** value, int data_size)
5187 {
5188  T_SET *set;
5189  int ele_type;
5190  int num_element;
5191  int err_code;
5192 
5193  if ((err_code = t_set_alloc (&set)) < 0)
5194  {
5195  return err_code;
5196  }
5197 
5198  if (!(CCI_IS_COLLECTION_TYPE (u_ext_type)))
5199  {
5200  return CCI_ER_TYPE_CONVERSION;
5201  }
5202 
5203  ele_type = *col_value_p;
5204  col_value_p++;
5205  data_size--;
5206  NET_STR_TO_INT (num_element, col_value_p);
5207  col_value_p += 4;
5208  data_size -= 4;
5209 
5210  set->type = ele_type;
5211  set->num_element = num_element;
5212 
5213  set->data_buf = MALLOC (data_size);
5214  if (set->data_buf == NULL)
5215  {
5216  t_set_free (set);
5217  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
5218  }
5219  memcpy (set->data_buf, col_value_p, data_size);
5220  set->data_size = data_size;
5221  if ((err_code = t_set_decode (set)) < 0)
5222  {
5223  t_set_free (set);
5224  return err_code;
5225  }
5226 
5227  *value = set;
5228  return 0;
5229 }

5246 static int
5247 get_column_info (char *buf_p, int *size, T_CCI_COL_INFO ** ret_col_info, char **next_buf_p, bool is_prepare)
5248 {
5249  char *cur_p = buf_p;
5250  int remain_size = *size;
5251  int num_col_info = 0;
5252  T_CCI_COL_INFO *col_info;
5253  int i;
5254 
5255  if (ret_col_info)
5256  {
5257  *ret_col_info = NULL;
5258  }
5259 
5260  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_INT)
5261  {
5262  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5263  }
5264 
5265  if (cur_p == NULL)
5266  {
5267  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5268  }
5269 
5270  NET_STR_TO_INT (num_col_info, cur_p);
5271  if (num_col_info < 0)
5272  {
5273  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5274  }
5275 
5276  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_INT;
5277  cur_p += NET_SIZE_INT;
5278 
5279  col_info = NULL;
5280  if (num_col_info > 0)
5281  {
5282  col_info = (T_CCI_COL_INFO *) MALLOC (sizeof (T_CCI_COL_INFO) * num_col_info);
5283  if (col_info == NULL)
5284  {
5285  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
5286  }
5287 
5288  memset ((char *) col_info, 0, sizeof (T_CCI_COL_INFO) * num_col_info);
5289 
5290  for (i = 0; i < num_col_info; i++)
5291  {
5292  int name_size;
5293  char type, set_type;
5294 
5295  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_BYTE)
5296  {
5297  goto get_column_info_error;
5298  }
5299  NET_STR_TO_BYTE (type, cur_p);
5300  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5301  cur_p += NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5302 
5303  if (CCI_NET_TYPE_HAS_2BYTES (type))
5304  {
5305  /* read two bytes for byte */
5306  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_BYTE)
5307  {
5308  goto get_column_info_error;
5309  }
5310  NET_STR_TO_BYTE (set_type, cur_p);
5311  col_info[i].ext_type = get_ext_utype_from_net_bytes ((T_CCI_U_TYPE) type, (T_CCI_U_TYPE) set_type);
5312  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5313  cur_p += NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5314  }
5315  else
5316  {
5317  /* legacy server : one byte */
5318  col_info[i].ext_type = type;
5319  }
5320 
5321  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_SHORT)
5322  {
5323  goto get_column_info_error;
5324  }
5325  NET_STR_TO_SHORT (col_info[i].scale, cur_p);
5326  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_SHORT;
5327  cur_p += NET_SIZE_SHORT;
5328 
5329  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_INT)
5330  {
5331  goto get_column_info_error;
5332  }
5333  NET_STR_TO_INT (col_info[i].precision, cur_p);
5334  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_INT;
5335  cur_p += NET_SIZE_INT;
5336 
5337  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_INT)
5338  {
5339  goto get_column_info_error;
5340  }
5341  NET_STR_TO_INT (name_size, cur_p);
5342  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_INT;
5343  cur_p += NET_SIZE_INT;
5344 
5345  if (remain_size < name_size)
5346  {
5347  goto get_column_info_error;
5348  }
5349  ALLOC_N_COPY (col_info[i].col_name, cur_p, name_size, char *);
5350  if (col_info[i].col_name == NULL)
5351  {
5352  goto get_column_info_error;
5353  }
5354  remain_size -= name_size;
5355  cur_p += name_size;
5356 
5357  if (is_prepare == false)
5358  {
5359  continue;
5360  }
5361 
5362  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_INT)
5363  {
5364  goto get_column_info_error;
5365  }
5366  NET_STR_TO_INT (name_size, cur_p);
5367  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_INT;
5368  cur_p += NET_SIZE_INT;
5369 
5370  if (remain_size < name_size)
5371  {
5372  goto get_column_info_error;
5373  }
5374  ALLOC_N_COPY (col_info[i].real_attr, cur_p, name_size, char *);
5375  remain_size -= name_size;
5376  cur_p += name_size;
5377 
5378  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_INT)
5379  {
5380  goto get_column_info_error;
5381  }
5382  NET_STR_TO_INT (name_size, cur_p);
5383  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_INT;
5384  cur_p += NET_SIZE_INT;
5385 
5386  if (remain_size < name_size)
5387  {
5388  goto get_column_info_error;
5389  }
5390  ALLOC_N_COPY (col_info[i].class_name, cur_p, name_size, char *);
5391  remain_size -= name_size;
5392  cur_p += name_size;
5393 
5394  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_BYTE)
5395  {
5396  goto get_column_info_error;
5397  }
5398  NET_STR_TO_BYTE (col_info[i].is_non_null, cur_p);
5399  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5400  cur_p += NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5401 
5402  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_INT)
5403  {
5404  goto get_column_info_error;
5405  }
5406  NET_STR_TO_INT (name_size, cur_p);
5407  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_INT;
5408  cur_p += NET_SIZE_INT;
5409 
5410  if (remain_size < name_size)
5411  {
5412  goto get_column_info_error;
5413  }
5414  ALLOC_N_COPY (col_info[i].default_value, cur_p, name_size, char *);
5415  if (col_info[i].default_value == NULL)
5416  {
5417  goto get_column_info_error;
5418  }
5419  remain_size -= name_size;
5420  cur_p += name_size;
5421 
5422  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_BYTE)
5423  {
5424  goto get_column_info_error;
5425  }
5426  col_info[i].is_auto_increment = *cur_p;
5427  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5428  cur_p += NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5429 
5430  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_BYTE)
5431  {
5432  goto get_column_info_error;
5433  }
5434  NET_STR_TO_BYTE (col_info[i].is_unique_key, cur_p);
5435  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5436  cur_p += NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5437 
5438  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_BYTE)
5439  {
5440  goto get_column_info_error;
5441  }
5442  NET_STR_TO_BYTE (col_info[i].is_primary_key, cur_p);
5443  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5444  cur_p += NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5445 
5446  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_BYTE)
5447  {
5448  goto get_column_info_error;
5449  }
5450  NET_STR_TO_BYTE (col_info[i].is_reverse_index, cur_p);
5451  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5452  cur_p += NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5453 
5454  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_BYTE)
5455  {
5456  goto get_column_info_error;
5457  }
5458  NET_STR_TO_BYTE (col_info[i].is_reverse_unique, cur_p);
5459  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5460  cur_p += NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5461 
5462  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_BYTE)
5463  {
5464  goto get_column_info_error;
5465  }
5466  NET_STR_TO_BYTE (col_info[i].is_foreign_key, cur_p);
5467  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5468  cur_p += NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5469 
5470  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_BYTE)
5471  {
5472  goto get_column_info_error;
5473  }
5474  NET_STR_TO_BYTE (col_info[i].is_shared, cur_p);
5475  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5476  cur_p += NET_SIZE_BYTE;
5477  }
5478  }
5479 
5480  if (ret_col_info)
5481  {
5482  *ret_col_info = col_info;
5483  }
5484 
5485  if (next_buf_p)
5486  {
5487  *next_buf_p = cur_p;
5488  }
5489 
5490  *size = remain_size;
5491  return num_col_info;
5492 
5493 get_column_info_error:
5494  if (col_info)
5495  {
5496  for (i = 0; i < num_col_info; i++)
5497  {
5498  FREE_MEM (col_info[i].col_name);
5499  FREE_MEM (col_info[i].real_attr);
5500  FREE_MEM (col_info[i].class_name);
5501  FREE_MEM (col_info[i].default_value);
5502  }
5503  FREE_MEM (col_info);
5504  }
5505 
5506  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5507 }

5509 static int
5510 oid_get_info_decode (char *buf_p, int remain_size, T_REQ_HANDLE * req_handle, T_CON_HANDLE * con_handle)
5511 {
5512  int num_col_info;
5513  int class_name_size;
5514  int err_code;
5515  char *class_name;
5516  char *cur_p = buf_p;
5517  int size;
5518  char *next_buf_p;
5519  T_CCI_COL_INFO *col_info = NULL;
5520 
5521  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_INT)
5522  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5523  NET_STR_TO_INT (class_name_size, cur_p);
5524  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_INT;
5525  cur_p += NET_SIZE_INT;
5526 
5527  if (remain_size < class_name_size || class_name_size <= 0)
5528  {
5529  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5530  }
5531 
5532  class_name = cur_p;
5533  remain_size -= class_name_size;
5534  cur_p += class_name_size;
5535 
5536  size = remain_size;
5537 
5538  num_col_info = get_column_info (cur_p, &size, &col_info, &next_buf_p, false);
5539  if (num_col_info < 0)
5540  {
5541  assert (col_info == NULL);
5542  return num_col_info;
5543  }
5544 
5545  req_handle->col_info = col_info;
5546  req_handle->num_col_info = num_col_info;
5547 
5548  remain_size -= CAST_STRLEN (next_buf_p - cur_p);
5549  err_code =
5550  fetch_info_decode (next_buf_p, remain_size, num_col_info, &(req_handle->tuple_value), FETCH_OID_GET, req_handle,
5551  con_handle);
5552  if (err_code < 0)
5553  {
5554  return err_code;
5555  }
5556 
5557  req_handle->fetched_tuple_end = req_handle->fetched_tuple_begin = 1;
5558  req_handle->cur_fetch_tuple_index = 0;
5559  req_handle->cursor_pos = 1;
5560  return 0;
5561 }

5570  int num_col_info;

5573  {
5574  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;

5576

5596 static int
5597 col_get_info_decode (char *buf_p, int remain_size, int *col_size, int *col_type, T_REQ_HANDLE * req_handle,
5598  T_CON_HANDLE * con_handle)
5599 {
5600  int num_col_info;
5601  char *cur_p = buf_p;
5602  char *next_buf_p;
5603  T_CCI_COL_INFO *col_info = NULL;
5604  int num_tuple;
5605  int size;
5606 
5607  if (remain_size < 1)
5608  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5609  if (col_type)
5610  {
5611  *col_type = *cur_p;
5612  }
5613  remain_size -= 1;
5614  cur_p += 1;
5615 
5616  size = remain_size;
5617  num_col_info = get_column_info (cur_p, &size, &col_info, &next_buf_p, false);
5618  if (num_col_info < 0)
5619  {
5620  assert (col_info == NULL);
5621  return num_col_info;
5622  }
5623 
5624  req_handle->col_info = col_info;
5625  req_handle->num_col_info = num_col_info;
5626 
5627  remain_size -= CAST_STRLEN (next_buf_p - cur_p);
5628  cur_p = next_buf_p;
5629 
5630  num_tuple =
5631  fetch_info_decode (cur_p, remain_size, 1, &(req_handle->tuple_value), FETCH_COL_GET, req_handle, con_handle);
5632  if (num_tuple < 0)
5633  return num_tuple;
5634 
5635  if (col_size)
5636  {
5637  *col_size = num_tuple;
5638  }
5639  req_handle->num_tuple = num_tuple;
5640  if (num_tuple == 0)
5641  {
5642  req_handle->fetched_tuple_begin = 0;
5643  req_handle->fetched_tuple_end = 0;
5644  req_handle->cur_fetch_tuple_index = -1;
5645  }
5646  else
5647  {
5648  req_handle->fetched_tuple_begin = 1;
5649  req_handle->fetched_tuple_end = num_tuple;
5650  req_handle->cur_fetch_tuple_index = 0;
5651  }
5652 
5653  return 0;
5654 }

5656 static int
5657 next_result_info_decode (char *buf, int size, T_REQ_HANDLE * req_handle)
5658 {
5659  int remain_size = size;
5660  char *cur_p = buf;
5661  int result_count;
5662  int num_col_info;
5663  char stmt_type;
5664  char updatable_flag;
5665  T_CCI_COL_INFO *col_info = NULL;
5666 
5667  if (remain_size < 4)
5668  {
5669  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5670  }
5671 
5672  NET_STR_TO_INT (result_count, cur_p);
5673  remain_size -= 4;
5674  cur_p += 4;
5675 
5676  if (remain_size < 1)
5677  {
5678  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5679  }
5680 
5681  stmt_type = *cur_p;
5682  remain_size -= 1;
5683  cur_p += 1;
5684 
5685  if (remain_size < 1)
5686  {
5687  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
5688  }
5689 
5690  updatable_flag = *cur_p;
5691  remain_size -= 1;
5692  cur_p += 1;
5693 
5694  size = remain_size;
5695  num_col_info = get_column_info (cur_p, &size, &col_info, NULL, true);
5696  if (num_col_info < 0)
5697  {
5698  assert (col_info == NULL);
5699  return num_col_info;
5700  }
5701 
5702  req_handle_col_info_free (req_handle);
5703 
5704  req_handle->num_tuple = result_count;
5705  req_handle->num_col_info = num_col_info;
5706  req_handle->col_info = col_info;
5707  req_handle->stmt_type = (T_CCI_CUBRID_STMT) stmt_type;
5708  req_handle->updatable_flag = updatable_flag;
5709 
5710  return result_count;
5711 }

5713 static int
5714 bind_value_conversion (T_CCI_A_TYPE a_type, T_CCI_U_TYPE u_type, char flag, void *value, int length,
5715  T_BIND_VALUE * bind_value)
5716 {
5717  int err_code;
5718 
5719  assert (u_type >= CCI_U_TYPE_FIRST && u_type <= CCI_U_TYPE_LAST);
5720 
5721  if (a_type == CCI_A_TYPE_STR)
5722  {
5723  switch (u_type)
5724  {
5725  case CCI_U_TYPE_CHAR:
5726  case CCI_U_TYPE_STRING:
5727  case CCI_U_TYPE_NCHAR:
5728  case CCI_U_TYPE_VARNCHAR:
5729  case CCI_U_TYPE_NUMERIC:
5730  case CCI_U_TYPE_ENUM:
5731  if (length == UNMEASURED_LENGTH)
5732  {
5733  bind_value->size = strlen ((const char *) value);
5734  }
5735  else
5736  {
5737  bind_value->size = length;
5738  }
5739 
5740  if (flag == CCI_BIND_PTR)
5741  {
5742  bind_value->flag = BIND_PTR_STATIC;
5743  bind_value->value = value;
5744  }
5745  else
5746  {
5747  bind_value->flag = BIND_PTR_DYNAMIC;
5748  ALLOC_COPY_BIT (bind_value->value, value, bind_value->size);
5749  if (bind_value->value == NULL)
5750  {
5751  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
5752  }
5753  }
5754 
5755  bind_value->size += 1; /* protocol with cas */
5756  break;
5757  case CCI_U_TYPE_BIGINT:
5758  {
5759  INT64 bi_val;
5760 
5761  err_code = ut_str_to_bigint ((char *) value, &bi_val);
5762  if (err_code < 0)
5763  {
5764  return err_code;
5765  }
5766  ALLOC_COPY_BIGINT (bind_value->value, bi_val);
5767  if (bind_value->value == NULL)
5768  {
5769  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
5770  }
5771  bind_value->size = sizeof (INT64);
5772  bind_value->flag = BIND_PTR_DYNAMIC;
5773  }
5774  break;
5775  case CCI_U_TYPE_UBIGINT:
5776  {
5777  UINT64 ubi_val;
5778

6403  ALLOC_COPY_INT (bind_value->value, (int) d_value);
6404  if (bind_value->value == NULL)
6405  {
6406  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
6407  }
6408  break;
6409  case CCI_U_TYPE_UINT:
6410  case CCI_U_TYPE_USHORT:
6411  ALLOC_COPY_UINT (bind_value->value, (unsigned int) d_value);
6412  if (bind_value->value == NULL)
6413  {
6414  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
6415  }
6416  break;
6417  case CCI_U_TYPE_MONETARY:
6418  case CCI_U_TYPE_DOUBLE:
6419  ALLOC_COPY_DOUBLE (bind_value->value, d_value);
6420  if (bind_value->value == NULL)
6421  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
6422  break;
6423  case CCI_U_TYPE_FLOAT:
6424  ALLOC_COPY_FLOAT (bind_value->value, (float) d_value);
6425  if (bind_value->value == NULL)
6426  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
6427  break;
6428  default:
6429  return CCI_ER_TYPE_CONVERSION;
6430  }
6431  bind_value->flag = BIND_PTR_DYNAMIC;
6432  }
6433  else if (a_type == CCI_A_TYPE_BIT)
6434  {
6435  switch (u_type)
6436  {
6437  case CCI_U_TYPE_BIT:
6438  case CCI_U_TYPE_VARBIT:
6439  {
6440  T_CCI_BIT *bit_value = (T_CCI_BIT *) value;
6441 
6442  if (flag == CCI_BIND_PTR)
6443  {
6444  bind_value->value = bit_value->buf;
6445  bind_value->flag = BIND_PTR_STATIC;
6446  }
6447  else
6448  {
6449  ALLOC_COPY_BIT (bind_value->value, bit_value->buf, bit_value->size);
6450  if (bind_value->value == NULL)
6451  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
6452  bind_value->flag = BIND_PTR_DYNAMIC;
6453  }
6454  bind_value->size = bit_value->size;
6455  }
6456  break;
6457  default:
6458  return CCI_ER_TYPE_CONVERSION;
6459  }
6460  }
6461  else if (a_type == CCI_A_TYPE_SET)
6462  {
6463  switch (u_type)
6464  {
6465  case CCI_U_TYPE_SET:
6466  case CCI_U_TYPE_MULTISET:
6467  case CCI_U_TYPE_SEQUENCE:
6468  {
6469  T_SET *set;
6470  set = (T_SET *) value;
6471  bind_value->value = MALLOC (set->data_size + 1);
6472  if (bind_value->value == NULL)
6473  {
6474  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
6475  }
6476  *((char *) (bind_value->value)) = set->type;
6477  memcpy ((char *) (bind_value->value) + 1, set->data_buf, set->data_size);
6478  bind_value->size = set->data_size + 1;
6479  bind_value->flag = BIND_PTR_DYNAMIC;
6480  }
6481  break;
6482  default:
6483  return CCI_ER_TYPE_CONVERSION;
6484  }
6485  }
6486  else if (a_type == CCI_A_TYPE_DATE)
6487  {
6488  switch (u_type)
6489  {
6490  case CCI_U_TYPE_DATE:
6491  case CCI_U_TYPE_TIME:
6492  case CCI_U_TYPE_TIMESTAMP:
6493  case CCI_U_TYPE_DATETIME:
6494  {
6495  ALLOC_COPY_DATE (bind_value->value, *((T_CCI_DATE *) value));
6496  if (bind_value->value == NULL)
6497  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
6498  bind_value->size = sizeof (T_CCI_DATE);
6499  bind_value->flag = BIND_PTR_DYNAMIC;
6500  }
6501  break;
6502  default:
6503  return CCI_ER_TYPE_CONVERSION;
6504  }
6505  }
6506  else if (a_type == CCI_A_TYPE_DATE_TZ)
6507  {
6508  switch (u_type)
6509  {
6510  case CCI_U_TYPE_TIMESTAMPTZ:
6511  case CCI_U_TYPE_TIMESTAMPLTZ:
6512  case CCI_U_TYPE_DATETIMETZ:
6513  case CCI_U_TYPE_DATETIMELTZ:
6514  {
6515  ALLOC_COPY_DATE_TZ (bind_value->value, *((T_CCI_DATE_TZ *) value));
6516  if (bind_value->value == NULL)
6517  {
6518  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
6519  }
6520  bind_value->size = sizeof (T_CCI_DATE) + NET_SIZE_TZ (value);
6521  bind_value->flag = BIND_PTR_DYNAMIC;
6522  }
6523  break;
6524  default:
6525  return CCI_ER_TYPE_CONVERSION;
6526  }
6527  }
6528  else if (a_type == CCI_A_TYPE_BLOB || a_type == CCI_A_TYPE_CLOB)
6529  {
6530  switch (u_type)
6531  {
6532  case CCI_U_TYPE_BLOB:
6533  case CCI_U_TYPE_CLOB:
6534  {
6535  ALLOC_COPY_BIT (bind_value->value, (T_LOB *) value, sizeof (T_LOB));
6536  bind_value->size = sizeof (T_LOB);
6537  bind_value->flag = BIND_PTR_DYNAMIC;
6538  }
6539  break;
6540  default:
6541  return CCI_ER_TYPE_CONVERSION;
6542  }
6543  }
6544  else
6545  {
6546  return CCI_ER_ATYPE;
6547  }
6548 
6549  bind_value->u_type = u_type;
6550  if (u_type == CCI_U_TYPE_SHORT)
6551  {
6552  bind_value->u_type = CCI_U_TYPE_INT;
6553  }
6554  else if (u_type == CCI_U_TYPE_USHORT)
6555  {
6556  bind_value->u_type = CCI_U_TYPE_UINT;
6557  }
6558 
6559  switch (u_type)
6560  {
6561  case CCI_U_TYPE_SHORT:
6562  case CCI_U_TYPE_INT:
6563  case CCI_U_TYPE_USHORT:
6564  case CCI_U_TYPE_UINT:
6565  bind_value->size = NET_SIZE_INT;
6566  break;
6567  case CCI_U_TYPE_BIGINT:
6568  case CCI_U_TYPE_UBIGINT:
6569  bind_value->size = NET_SIZE_BIGINT;
6570  break;
6571  case CCI_U_TYPE_MONETARY:
6572  case CCI_U_TYPE_DOUBLE:
6573  bind_value->size = NET_SIZE_DOUBLE;
6574  break;
6575  case CCI_U_TYPE_FLOAT:
6576  bind_value->size = NET_SIZE_FLOAT;
6577  break;
6578  case CCI_U_TYPE_DATE:
6579  bind_value->size = NET_SIZE_DATE;
6580  break;
6581  case CCI_U_TYPE_TIME:
6582  bind_value->size = NET_SIZE_TIME;
6583  break;
6584  case CCI_U_TYPE_TIMESTAMP:
6585  bind_value->size = NET_SIZE_TIMESTAMP;
6586  break;
6587  case CCI_U_TYPE_DATETIME:
6588  bind_value->size = NET_SIZE_DATETIME;
6589  break;
6590  case CCI_U_TYPE_OBJECT:
6591  bind_value->size = NET_SIZE_OBJECT;
6592  break;
6593  case CCI_U_TYPE_TIMESTAMPTZ:
6594  case CCI_U_TYPE_TIMESTAMPLTZ:
6595  bind_value->size = NET_SIZE_TIMESTAMP + NET_SIZE_TZ (bind_value->value);
6596  break;
6597  case CCI_U_TYPE_DATETIMETZ:
6598  case CCI_U_TYPE_DATETIMELTZ:
6599  bind_value->size = NET_SIZE_DATETIME + NET_SIZE_TZ (bind_value->value);
6600  break;
6601  default:
6602  break;
6603  }
6604 
6605  return 0;
6606 }
6607 
6608 static int
6609 bind_value_to_net_buf (T_NET_BUF * net_buf, T_CCI_U_TYPE u_type, void *value, int size, char *charset,
6610  bool set_default_value)
6611 {
6612  if (u_type < CCI_U_TYPE_FIRST || u_type > CCI_U_TYPE_LAST)
6613  {
6614  u_type = CCI_U_TYPE_NULL;
6615  }
6616 
6617  if (u_type != CCI_U_TYPE_NULL && value == NULL && set_default_value == false)
6618  {
6619  assert (false);
6620  u_type = CCI_U_TYPE_NULL;
6621  ADD_ARG_BYTES (net_buf, &u_type, 1);
6622  ADD_ARG_BYTES (net_buf, NULL, 0);
6623  return 0;
6624  }
6625 
6626  ADD_ARG_BYTES (net_buf, &u_type, 1);
6627 
6628  switch (u_type)
6629  {
6630  case CCI_U_TYPE_CHAR:
6631  case CCI_U_TYPE_STRING:
6632  case CCI_U_TYPE_NCHAR:
6633  case CCI_U_TYPE_VARNCHAR:
6634  case CCI_U_TYPE_ENUM:
6635  if (value == NULL)
6636  {
6637  ADD_ARG_BIND_STR (net_buf, "", 1, charset);
6638  }
6639  else
6640  {
6641  ADD_ARG_BIND_STR (net_buf, (char *) value, size, charset);
6642  }
6643  break;
6644  case CCI_U_TYPE_NUMERIC:
6645  if (value == NULL)
6646  {
6647  ADD_ARG_BYTES (net_buf, NULL, 0);
6648  }
6649  else
6650  {
6651  ADD_ARG_BIND_STR (net_buf, (char *) value, size, charset);
6652  }
6653  break;
6654  case CCI_U_TYPE_SET:
6655  case CCI_U_TYPE_MULTISET:
6656  case CCI_U_TYPE_SEQUENCE:
6657  if (value == NULL)
6658  {
6659  ADD_ARG_BYTES (net_buf, NULL, 0);
6660  }
6661  else
6662  {
6663  ADD_ARG_BYTES (net_buf, value, size);
6664  }
6665  break;
6666  case CCI_U_TYPE_BIT:
6667  case CCI_U_TYPE_VARBIT:
6668  if (value == NULL)
6669  {
6670  char empty_byte = 0;
6671  ADD_ARG_BYTES (net_buf, &empty_byte, 1);
6672  }
6673  else
6674  {
6675  ADD_ARG_BYTES (net_buf, value, size);
6676  }
6677  break;
6678  case CCI_U_TYPE_BIGINT:
6679  case CCI_U_TYPE_UBIGINT:
6680  if (value == NULL)
6681  {
6682  ADD_ARG_BIGINT (net_buf, 0LL);
6683  }
6684  else
6685  {
6686  ADD_ARG_BIGINT (net_buf, *((INT64 *) value));
6687  }
6688  break;
6689  case CCI_U_TYPE_INT:
6690  case CCI_U_TYPE_SHORT:
6691  case CCI_U_TYPE_UINT:
6692  case CCI_U_TYPE_USHORT:
6693  if (value == NULL)
6694  {
6695  ADD_ARG_INT (net_buf, 0);
6696  }
6697  else
6698  {
6699  ADD_ARG_INT (net_buf, *((int *) value));
6700  }
6701  break;
6702  case CCI_U_TYPE_FLOAT:
6703  if (value == NULL)
6704  {
6705  ADD_ARG_FLOAT (net_buf, 0.0f);
6706  }
6707  else
6708  {
6709  ADD_ARG_FLOAT (net_buf, *((float *) value));
6710  }
6711  break;
6712  case CCI_U_TYPE_MONETARY:
6713  case CCI_U_TYPE_DOUBLE:
6714  if (value == NULL)
6715  {
6716  ADD_ARG_DOUBLE (net_buf, 0.0l);
6717  }
6718  else
6719  {
6720  ADD_ARG_DOUBLE (net_buf, *((double *) value));
6721  }
6722  break;
6723  case CCI_U_TYPE_DATE:
6724  case CCI_U_TYPE_TIME:
6725  case CCI_U_TYPE_TIMESTAMP:
6726  case CCI_U_TYPE_DATETIME:
6727  if (value == NULL)
6728  {
6729  T_CCI_DATE default_value;
6730  default_value.yr = 1970;
6731  default_value.mon = 1;
6732  default_value.day = 1;
6733  default_value.hh = 0;
6734  default_value.mm = 0;
6735  default_value.ss = 0;
6736  default_value.ms = 0;
6737  ADD_ARG_DATETIME (net_buf, &default_value);
6738  }
6739  else
6740  {
6741  ADD_ARG_DATETIME (net_buf, value);
6742  }
6743  break;
6744  case CCI_U_TYPE_TIMESTAMPTZ:
6745  case CCI_U_TYPE_TIMESTAMPLTZ:
6746  case CCI_U_TYPE_DATETIMETZ:
6747  case CCI_U_TYPE_DATETIMELTZ:
6748  if (value == NULL)
6749  {
6750  T_CCI_DATE_TZ default_value;
6751  default_value.yr = 1970;
6752  default_value.mon = 1;
6753  default_value.day = 1;
6754  default_value.hh = 0;
6755  default_value.mm = 0;
6756  default_value.ss = 0;
6757  default_value.tz[0] = '\0';
6758  ADD_ARG_DATETIMETZ (net_buf, &default_value);
6759  }
6760  else
6761  {
6762  ADD_ARG_DATETIMETZ (net_buf, value);
6763  }
6764  break;
6765  case CCI_U_TYPE_OBJECT:
6766  if (value == NULL)
6767  {
6768  ADD_ARG_BYTES (net_buf, NULL, 0);
6769  }
6770  else
6771  {
6772  ADD_ARG_OBJECT (net_buf, value);
6773  }
6774  break;
6775  case CCI_U_TYPE_BLOB:
6776  case CCI_U_TYPE_CLOB:
6777  if (value == NULL)
6778  {
6779  ADD_ARG_BYTES (net_buf, NULL, 0);
6780  }
6781  else
6782  {
6783  ADD_ARG_LOB (net_buf, value);
6784  }
6785  break;
6786  default:
6787  ADD_ARG_BYTES (net_buf, NULL, 0);
6788  break;
6789  }
6790 
6791  return 0;
6792 }
6793 
6794 static int
6795 execute_array_info_decode (char *buf, int size, char flag, T_CCI_QUERY_RESULT ** res_qr, int *res_remain_size)
6796 {
6797  int remain_size = size;
6798  char *cur_p = buf;
6799  int num_query;
6800  int res_count;
6801  int i;
6802  T_OBJECT oid;
6803  T_CCI_QUERY_RESULT *qr;
6804  char client_cache_reusable;
6805 
6806  if (flag == EXECUTE_EXEC)
6807  {
6808  if (remain_size < 1)
6809  {
6810  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
6811  }
6812  client_cache_reusable = *cur_p;
6813  remain_size -= 1;
6814  cur_p += 1;
6815  }
6816 
6817  if (remain_size < 4)
6818  {
6819  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
6820  }
6821 
6822  if (cur_p == NULL)
6823  {
6824  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
6825  }
6826 
6827  NET_STR_TO_INT (num_query, cur_p);
6828  if (num_query < 0)
6829  {
6830  assert (0);
6831  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
6832  }
6833 
6834  remain_size -= 4;
6835  cur_p += 4;
6836 
6837  if (num_query == 0)
6838  {
6839  assert (0);
6840  *res_qr = NULL;
6841  *res_remain_size = remain_size;
6842 
6843  return num_query;
6844  }
6845 
6846  qr = (T_CCI_QUERY_RESULT *) MALLOC (sizeof (T_CCI_QUERY_RESULT) * num_query);
6847  if (qr == NULL)
6848  {
6849  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
6850  }
6851 
6852  memset (qr, 0, sizeof (T_CCI_QUERY_RESULT) * num_query);
6853 
6854  for (i = 0; i < num_query; i++)
6855  {
6856  if (flag == EXECUTE_BATCH || flag == EXECUTE_EXEC)
6857  {
6858  if (remain_size < 1)
6859  {
6860  qe_query_result_free (i, qr);
6861  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
6862  }
6863 
6864  qr[i].stmt_type = *cur_p;
6865  remain_size -= 1;
6866  cur_p += 1;
6867  }
6868 
6869  if (remain_size < 4)
6870  {
6871  qe_query_result_free (i, qr);
6872  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
6873  }
6874 
6875  NET_STR_TO_INT (res_count, cur_p);
6876  remain_size -= 4;
6877  cur_p += 4;
6878 
6879  qr[i].result_count = res_count;
6880 
6881  if (res_count < 0)
6882  {
6883  int err_code;
6884  int err_msg_size;
6885 
6886  if (remain_size < 4)
6887  {
6888  qe_query_result_free (i, qr);
6889  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
6890  }
6891 
6892  NET_STR_TO_INT (err_code, cur_p);
6893  remain_size -= 4;
6894  cur_p += 4;
6895 
6896  qr[i].err_no = err_code;
6897 
6898  if (remain_size < 4)
6899  {
6900  qe_query_result_free (i, qr);
6901  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
6902  }
6903 
6904  NET_STR_TO_INT (err_msg_size, cur_p);
6905  remain_size -= 4;
6906  cur_p += 4;
6907 
6908  if (err_msg_size > 0)
6909  {
6910  if (remain_size < err_msg_size)
6911  {
6912  qe_query_result_free (i, qr);
6913  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
6914  }
6915 
6916  ALLOC_N_COPY (qr[i].err_msg, cur_p, err_msg_size, char *);
6917  remain_size -= err_msg_size;
6918  cur_p += err_msg_size;
6919  }
6920  }
6921  else
6922  {
6923  if (remain_size < NET_SIZE_OBJECT)
6924  {
6925  qe_query_result_free (i, qr);
6926  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
6927  }
6928 
6929  NET_STR_TO_OBJECT (oid, cur_p);
6930  ut_oid_to_str (&oid, qr[i].oid);
6931  cur_p += NET_SIZE_OBJECT;
6932  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_OBJECT;
6933 
6934  if (flag == EXECUTE_EXEC)
6935  {
6936  int cache_time_sec, cache_time_usec;
6937  if (remain_size < 8)
6938  {
6939  qe_query_result_free (i, qr);
6940  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
6941  }
6942 
6943  NET_STR_TO_INT (cache_time_sec, cur_p);
6944  NET_STR_TO_INT (cache_time_usec, cur_p + 4);
6945  remain_size -= 8;
6946  cur_p += 8;
6947  }
6948  }
6949  }
6950 
6951  *res_qr = qr;
6952  *res_remain_size = remain_size;
6953 
6954  return num_query;
6955 }
6956 
6957 static T_CCI_U_TYPE
6958 get_basic_utype (T_CCI_U_EXT_TYPE u_ext_type)
6959 {
6960  if (CCI_IS_SET_TYPE (u_ext_type))
6961  {
6962  return CCI_U_TYPE_SET;
6963  }
6964  else if (CCI_IS_MULTISET_TYPE (u_ext_type))
6965  {
6966  return CCI_U_TYPE_MULTISET;
6967  }
6968  else if (CCI_IS_SEQUENCE_TYPE (u_ext_type))
6969  {
6970  return CCI_U_TYPE_SEQUENCE;
6971  }
6972  else
6973  {
6974  return (T_CCI_U_TYPE) CCI_GET_COLLECTION_DOMAIN (u_ext_type);
6975  }
6976 }
6977 
6978 static int
6979 parameter_info_decode (char *buf, int size, int num_param, T_CCI_PARAM_INFO ** res_param)
6980 {
6981  T_CCI_PARAM_INFO *param;
6982  int i;
6983 
6984  param = (T_CCI_PARAM_INFO *) MALLOC (sizeof (T_CCI_PARAM_INFO) * num_param);
6985  if (param == NULL)
6986  {
6987  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
6988  }
6989  memset (param, 0, sizeof (T_CCI_PARAM_INFO) * num_param);
6990 
6991  for (i = 0; i < num_param; i++)
6992  {
6993  T_CCI_U_TYPE basic_type, set_type;
6994 
6995  if (size < 1)
6996  {
6997  goto param_decode_error;
6998  }
6999  param[i].mode = (T_CCI_PARAM_MODE) (*buf);
7000  size -= 1;
7001  buf += 1;
7002 
7003  if (size < 1)
7004  {
7005  goto param_decode_error;
7006  }
7007  basic_type = (T_CCI_U_TYPE) (*buf);
7008  size -= 1;
7009  buf += 1;
7010 
7011  if (CCI_NET_TYPE_HAS_2BYTES (basic_type))
7012  {
7013  if (size < 1)
7014  {
7015  goto param_decode_error;
7016  }
7017 
7018  /* type is encoded with 2 bytes */
7019  set_type = (T_CCI_U_TYPE) * buf;
7020  size -= 1;
7021  buf += 1;
7022 
7023  param[i].ext_type = get_ext_utype_from_net_bytes (basic_type, set_type);
7024  }
7025  else
7026  {
7027  /* legacy server : one byte */
7028  param[i].ext_type = basic_type;
7029  }
7030 
7031  if (size < 2)
7032  {
7033  goto param_decode_error;
7034  }
7035  NET_STR_TO_SHORT (param[i].scale, buf);
7036  size -= 2;
7037  buf += 2;
7038 
7039  if (size < 4)
7040  {
7041  goto param_decode_error;
7042  }
7043  NET_STR_TO_INT (param[i].precision, buf);
7044  size -= 4;
7045  buf += 4;
7046  }
7047 
7048  *res_param = param;
7049 
7050  return 0;
7051 
7052 param_decode_error:
7053  qe_param_info_free (param);
7054  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
7055 }
7056 
7057 static int
7058 decode_fetch_result (T_CON_HANDLE * con_handle, T_REQ_HANDLE * req_handle, char *result_msg_org, char *result_msg_start,
7059  int result_msg_size)
7060 {
7061  int num_cols;
7062  int num_tuple;
7063 
7064  if (req_handle->stmt_type == CUBRID_STMT_CALL_SP)
7065  {
7066  num_cols = req_handle->num_bind + 1;
7067  }
7068  else
7069  {
7070  num_cols = req_handle->num_col_info;
7071  }
7072 
7073  num_tuple =
7074  fetch_info_decode (result_msg_start, result_msg_size, num_cols, &(req_handle->tuple_value), FETCH_FETCH, req_handle,
7075  con_handle);
7076  if (num_tuple < 0)
7077  {
7078  return num_tuple;
7079  }
7080 
7081  if (num_tuple == 0)
7082  {
7083  req_handle->fetched_tuple_begin = 0;
7084  req_handle->fetched_tuple_end = 0;
7085  req_handle->msg_buf = result_msg_org;
7086  req_handle->cur_fetch_tuple_index = -1;
7087  }
7088  else
7089  {
7090  req_handle->fetched_tuple_begin = req_handle->cursor_pos;
7091  req_handle->fetched_tuple_end = req_handle->cursor_pos + num_tuple - 1;
7092  req_handle->msg_buf = result_msg_org;
7093  req_handle->cur_fetch_tuple_index = 0;
7094  }
7095 
7096  return num_tuple;
7097 }

7099 #ifdef CCI_XA
7100 static void
7101 add_arg_xid (T_NET_BUF * net_buf, XID * xid)
7102 {
7103  net_buf_cp_int (net_buf, 12 + xid->gtrid_length + xid->bqual_length);
7104  net_buf_cp_int (net_buf, xid->formatID);
7105  net_buf_cp_int (net_buf, xid->gtrid_length);
7106  net_buf_cp_int (net_buf, xid->bqual_length);
7107  net_buf_cp_str (net_buf, xid->data, xid->gtrid_length + xid->bqual_length);
7108 }
7109 
7110 static int
7111 xa_prepare_info_decode (char *buf, int buf_size, int count, XID * xid, int num_xid_buf)
7112 {
7113  int xid_data_size;
7114  int i;
7115 
7116  if (count > num_xid_buf)
7117  count = num_xid_buf;
7118 
7119  for (i = 0; i < count; i++)
7120  {
7121  if (buf_size < 4)
7122  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
7123  NET_STR_TO_INT (xid_data_size, buf);
7124  buf += 4;
7125  buf_size -= 4;
7126  if (buf_size < xid_data_size)
7127  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
7128  net_str_to_xid (buf, &(xid[i]));
7129  buf += xid_data_size;
7130  buf_size -= xid_data_size;
7131  }
7132 
7133  return count;
7134 }
7135 
7136 static void
7137 net_str_to_xid (char *buf, XID * xid)
7138 {
7139  memset (xid, 0, sizeof (XID));
7140  NET_STR_TO_INT (xid->formatID, buf);
7141  buf += 4;
7142  NET_STR_TO_INT (xid->gtrid_length, buf);
7143  buf += 4;
7144  NET_STR_TO_INT (xid->bqual_length, buf);
7145  buf += 4;
7146  memcpy (xid->data, buf, xid->gtrid_length + xid->bqual_length);
7147 }
7148 #endif
7149 
7150 static int
7151 shard_info_decode (char *buf_p, int size, int num_shard, T_CCI_SHARD_INFO ** res_shard_info)
7152 {
7153  T_CCI_SHARD_INFO *shard_info = NULL;
7154  char *cur_p = buf_p;
7155  int remain_size = size;
7156  int num_shard_tmp;
7157  int str_size;
7158  int i;
7159 
7160  num_shard_tmp = num_shard + 1 /* fence */ ;
7161 
7162  if (res_shard_info == NULL)
7163  {
7164  return CCI_ER_INVALID_ARGS;
7165  }
7166 
7167  shard_info = (T_CCI_SHARD_INFO *) MALLOC (sizeof (T_CCI_SHARD_INFO) * num_shard_tmp);
7168  if (shard_info == NULL)
7169  {
7170  return CCI_ER_NO_MORE_MEMORY;
7171  }
7172 
7173  for (i = 0; i < num_shard_tmp; i++)
7174  {
7175  shard_info[i].shard_id = SHARD_ID_INVALID;
7176  shard_info[i].db_name = NULL;
7177  shard_info[i].db_server = NULL;
7178  }
7179 
7180  for (i = 0; i < num_shard; i++)
7181  {
7182  if (remain_size < 4)
7183  {
7184  goto shard_info_decode_error;
7185  }
7186 
7187  /* shard id */
7188  NET_STR_TO_INT (shard_info[i].shard_id, cur_p);
7189  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_INT;
7190  cur_p += NET_SIZE_INT;
7191 
7192  /* shard real db name */
7193  NET_STR_TO_INT (str_size, cur_p);
7194  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_INT;
7195  cur_p += NET_SIZE_INT;
7196  if (remain_size < str_size)
7197  {
7198  goto shard_info_decode_error;
7199  }
7200  ALLOC_N_COPY (shard_info[i].db_name, cur_p, str_size, char *);
7201  if (shard_info[i].db_name == NULL)
7202  {
7203  goto shard_info_decode_error;
7204  }
7205  remain_size -= str_size;
7206  cur_p += str_size;
7207 
7208  /* shard read db server */
7209  NET_STR_TO_INT (str_size, cur_p);
7210  remain_size -= NET_SIZE_INT;
7211  cur_p += NET_SIZE_INT;
7212  if (remain_size < str_size)
7213  {
7214  goto shard_info_decode_error;
7215  }
7216  ALLOC_N_COPY (shard_info[i].db_server, cur_p, str_size, char *);
7217  if (shard_info[i].db_server == NULL)
7218  {
7219  goto shard_info_decode_error;
7220  }
7221  remain_size -= str_size;
7222  cur_p += str_size;
7223  }
7224 
7225  assert (remain_size == 0);
7226 
7227  *(res_shard_info) = shard_info;
7228  return CCI_ER_NO_ERROR;
7229 
7230 shard_info_decode_error:
7231  if (shard_info)
7232  {
7233  qe_shard_info_free (shard_info);
7234  shard_info = NULL;
7235  }
7236 
7237  return CCI_ER_COMMUNICATION;
7238 }

7259 
7260 /* get_ext_utype_from_net_bytes - creates an internal CCI extended type from
7261  * bytes received from network
7262  * input bits: basic_type : 0CCR RRRR
7263  * set_type : TTTT TTTT
7264  * output bits : TCCT TTTT
7265  * Only 6 bits from set_type are retained
7266  * (enough for 63 values)
7267  *
7268  */
7269 static T_CCI_U_EXT_TYPE
7270 get_ext_utype_from_net_bytes (T_CCI_U_TYPE basic_type, T_CCI_U_TYPE set_type)
7271 {
7272  T_CCI_U_EXT_TYPE ext_type_lsb, ext_type_msb, ext_type_cc, ext_type;
7273 
7274  ext_type_lsb = set_type & 0x1f;
7275  ext_type_msb = (set_type & 0x20) << 2;
7276  ext_type_cc = basic_type & CCI_CODE_COLLECTION;
7277 
7278  ext_type = ext_type_msb | ext_type_cc | ext_type_lsb;
7279 
7280  return ext_type;
7281 }

7283 static void
7284 confirm_schema_type_info (T_REQ_HANDLE * req_handle, int col_no, T_CCI_U_TYPE u_type, char *col_value_p, int data_size)
7285 {
7286 #define SCHEMA_INFO_TYPE_COL_INDEX 2
7287 
7288  if (req_handle->handle_type == HANDLE_SCHEMA_INFO
7289  && (req_handle->handle_sub_type == CCI_SCH_ATTRIBUTE || req_handle->handle_sub_type == CCI_SCH_CLASS_ATTRIBUTE)
7290  && col_no == SCHEMA_INFO_TYPE_COL_INDEX)
7291  {
7292  unsigned short value, net_val;
7293  assert (u_type == CCI_U_TYPE_SHORT);
7294  assert (data_size == NET_SIZE_SHORT);
7295 
7296  NET_STR_TO_USHORT (value, col_value_p);
7297 
7298  value = value & ~(CCI_CODE_COLLECTION << 8);
7299  value = value & ~(CAS_TYPE_FIRST_BYTE_PROTOCOL_MASK << 8);
7300 
7301  net_val = htons (value);
7302  memcpy (col_value_p, (char *) &net_val, NET_SIZE_SHORT);
7303  }
7304 
7305 #undef SCHEMA_INFO_TYPE_COL_INDEX
7306 }
